"persone che hanno fatto una grande differenza per noi."

#: metabrainz/templates/index/sponsors.html:42
#, fuzzy, python-format
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(google_url)s\">Google</a></b> has been an extremely "
"supportive\n"
"    sponsor, donating over <b>$500,000</b> over the years. Richard Jones "
"of\n"
"    <a href=\"%(last_fm_url)s\">Last.fm fame</a> donated <b>$50,000</b> "
"in 2010,\n"
"    <a href=\"%(oracle_url)s\">Sun Microsystems</a> &amp; Paul Lamere "
"donated a database\n"
"    server and <a href=\"%(oreilly_url)s\">O'Reilly Media</a> gave "
